# SDPA shapes: Q_dims:K_dims:V_dims
# Format: batch x heads x seq_q x head_size : batch x heads x head_size x seq_k : batch x heads x seq_k x head_v
#
# Standard MHA shapes (batch=1, heads=1, small sizes for smoke testing)

# Basic 2D (no batch): queries x head_size : head_size x keys : keys x values
4x8:8x4:4x8
8x16:16x8:8x16

# 3D (single batch dim): batch x queries x head_size : batch x head_size x keys : batch x keys x values
2x4x8:2x8x4:2x4x8
1x8x16:1x16x8:1x8x16

# 4D (batch x heads): typical transformer shapes
1x1x4x8:1x1x8x4:1x1x4x8
1x2x8x16:1x2x16x8:1x2x8x16
2x4x16x32:2x4x32x16:2x4x16x32
1x8x32x64:1x8x64x32:1x8x32x64

# Asymmetric seq lengths (seq_q != seq_k) - common in KV cache scenarios
1x1x1x64:1x1x64x128:1x1x128x64
1x4x1x64:1x4x64x256:1x4x256x64
